name: Brimming With Joy
description:
A droplet is caught between the unopened blooms of a Lilac sprig. The Lilac is a symbol of early growth, renewal, confidence, first love, magic and the transition from innocence to wisdom. (Syringa vulgaris)

This piece is a gift and a thank you to my top 21 collectors in 2021.

It has been an incredible few months, and this token is a reflection of my appreciation for your support of my work!

2019. Nikon D60, 55-200mm Lens.

Photographed in situ, without the use of artificial lighting or staging. Photoshop only used for resizing.

1024x685 300dpi jpeg
